Trade/Device Name(s): Stat Profile Prime ES Comp Plus Analyzer System
Regulation Name(s): Analyzer, chemistry (photometric, discrete), for clinical use
Instrument(s)/Platform(s): Stat Profile Prime ES Comp Plus Analyzer
Document Summary: FDA 510(k) summary for Stat Profile Prime ES Comp Plus Analyzer System for quantitative measurement of sodium, potassium, and chloride using ion selective electrode technology in clinical laboratory settings
Indications for Use Summary: For in vitro diagnostic use by healthcare professionals in clinical laboratory settings for quantitative determination of sodium, potassium, and chloride in heparinized venous whole blood, plasma, and serum
